https://www.npmjs.com/package/exceljs - To download exceljs through the terminal.

Move to the directory/folder where you plan to install exceljs. 
Enter npm init
Press enter multiple times until you're prompted with a yes?
Write yes and press Enter
On the terminal, type in npm install exceljs --savedev to install exceljs

https://rahulshettyacademy.com/upload-download-test/index.html - To download test template

On the VS terminal, go to the directory where this project is located and enter node ExcelDemo.js to run the test file